author: Carrie Wells
title: Ivanka Trump attends Monster Jam truck rally in Baltimore
text:
Lifestyle Baltimore Insider Ivanka Trump attends Monster Jam truck rally in Baltimore Carrie Wells showing her and one of her sons at the truck rally. In one, she poses with her son and a monster truck driver in front of a massively-wheeled truck that resembles a shark. In another photo, she holds her son behind the wheel of another monster truck.
"Epic first Monster Truck show with the kids!" she tweeted.
